<paragraph id="A0D1B37F0CCD6131830D24010F7165BB" pageId="0" pageNumber="1">
BRAZIL. 
<normalizedToken id="2A9AB44FAC2F5559F8865A3CDB64F413" originalValue="Goiás">Goias</normalizedToken>
, P.N. Chapada dos Veadeiros, ca. 1100 m, perto da sede do parque, 
<emphasis id="F33C1FC2D6AE6688B94BF50BBBEA50C6" italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="1">J.R. Pirani, R.M. Harley, B.L. Stannard, A. Furlan &amp; C. Kameyama</emphasis>
